      • codec_ids

        @MemberGetter
@Cast(value="const AVCodecID*")
public IntPointer codec_ids()
        A list of codec ids supported by the filter, terminated by AV_CODEC_ID_NONE. May be NULL, in that case the bitstream filter works with any codec id.

      • priv_class

        @MemberGetter
@Const
public avutil.AVClass priv_class()
        A class for the private data, used to declare bitstream filter private AVOptions. This field is NULL for bitstream filters that do not declare any options. If this field is non-NULL, the first member of the filter private data must be a pointer to AVClass, which will be set by libavcodec generic code to this class.
